These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, cucumber, avocado, carrot
4 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, rat, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, scooter, bus, ship
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person driving the ship is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the goat is between the person driving the bus and the person eating cucumber##2
6. the person driving the scooter is the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | avocado | carrot  | cucumber | pomegranate  |
| Pet         | rabbit    | goat  | hamster       | rat     |
| Transport   | bus     | tram | ship       | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, camping, rock-climbing, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, epic, family, spy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, baseball, tennis, cricket
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person watching spy movies and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
5. the person watching spy movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the person watching family movies is the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | camping | dancing    | collecting  | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | mystery  | epic   | family    |
| Sport         | baseball | cricket | skiing | tennis      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk, water, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, puzzles, chess, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, pop, funk, r&b
1. the fan of pop is between the fan of r&b and the person drinking milk##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the fan of blues##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
6. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | milk | juice         | soy-milk   | water    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | writing | video-games | chess |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | pop        | r&b      | blues   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, brazilian, french, american
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, soccer, water-polo, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, helicopter, roller
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the roller and the american##2
3. the french is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the french is on the right of the malaysian##1
6. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person driving the motorbike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | american        | brazilian   | malaysian | french |
| Sport         | water-polo | swimming | soccer    | surfing |
| Transport     | helicopter       | bike     | roller       | motorbike    |

