.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, soy-milk, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, baking, writing, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, water-polo, rugby, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking water##2
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola      | water       | soy-milk   |
| Hobby      | chess   | baking  | filmmaking | writing     |
| Sport      | water-polo     | lacrosse | rugby        | parkour |

