.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, pumpkin, pepper, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling, reading, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, skiing, rugby, handball
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's sport is rugby##2
6. the person eating pumpkin is between the person eating pomegranate and the person eating pepper##2
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | pepper | pumpkin  | pomegranate | tomato      |
| Hobby   | reading  | puzzles  | magic-tricks | traveling |
| Sport   | handball | surfing | skiing | rugby     |

