1. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching family movies##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person eating strawberry is between the person watching family movies and the person watching sports movies##2
7. the person eating pear is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
