.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, dancing, video-games, rock-climbing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, satire, documentary, mystery
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, dog, turtle
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the person watching satire movies is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing  | dancing | video-games | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | mystery | satire   | documentary         |
| Pet           | cat | dog  | hedgehog   | turtle      |

