.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, apricot, kale, carrot
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, fishing, baking, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, jazz, folk, indie
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person eating radish##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is the person eating apricot##1
5. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the fan of folk and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | carrot  | radish    | kale | apricot       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | fishing | skydiving  | baking |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | indie      | jazz  | blues     |

