The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, drawing, camping, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, family, action, disaster
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
3. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating papaya and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person watching romance movies is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | strawberry      | lemon | asparagus | papaya |
| Hobby         | cooking   | drawing  | video-games | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | romance   | family | action |

