.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, grapefruit, lime, banana
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, sudoku, fishing, rock-climbing
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, ferret, lizard
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the owner of the ferret is the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the owner of the rabbit and the person eating banana##2
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is the owner of the lizard##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is the owner of the horse##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | banana  | lime | pineapple | grapefruit     |
| Hobby   | singing | fishing   | rock-climbing  | sudoku    |
| Pet     | horse        | lizard       | rabbit      | ferret |

