.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, iced-tea, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, woodworking, drawing, collecting
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, lizard, dog
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea | iced-tea     | soy-milk | coffee       |
| Hobby      | drawing  | collecting | camping  | woodworking |
| Pet        | dog  | chinchilla      | lizard        | hedgehog      |

