3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the videographer##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is between the person watching sports movies and the doctor##2
6. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
