.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, juice, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, classical, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, polish, colombian, japanese
1. the fan of gospel is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking juice and the polish##2
3. the person drinking juice is the fan of pop##1
4. the person drinking juice is between the fan of classical and the japanese##2
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
6. the canadian is between the colombian and the fan of punk##2
7. the fan of gospel is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee | juice | sprite   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | pop    | classical   | punk     |
| Nationality   | japanese  | colombian | canadian | polish   |

