.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, water, milk
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, spinach, cauliflower, potato
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, cycling, climbing, snowboarding
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is climbing##2
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
7. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite    | cola | milk           | water |
| Food       | cranberry | cauliflower    | spinach          | potato   |
| Sport      | climbing  | cycling   | snowboarding | skiing  |

