The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, adventure, crime, thriller
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, guinea-pig, goat
1. the person watching crime movies is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching horror movies##2
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the owner of the goat is between the person drinking water and the owner of the chinchilla##2
7. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | cola | almond-milk | water     | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | thriller        | crime  | adventure  |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | goat         | pony | guinea-pig |

