3. the bartender is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the bike is the accountant##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the trike is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | bartender        | accountant  | photographer | writer   |
| Sport       | cycling | cricket | rugby    | sailing |
| Transport   | ship        | bike     | trike       | motorbike      |

