.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, broccoli, carrot, corn
4 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, goat, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, bike, snowmobile, bus
1. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the bus is the owner of the rat##1
6. the owner of the fish is between the person eating corn and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | corn | broccoli | tomato | carrot |
| Pet         | turtle       | fish     | goat   | rat   |
| Transport   | taxi | bike | snowmobile | bus |

 